---
title: Chorizo Taco Bowls with Red Lentil Rice and Lime Crema
description: Deconstructed tacos make for a hearty and filling supper with the help of lentils and rice! Topped with chorizo and peppers, fresh tomatoes, cheese and a lime crema, this bowl hits all the spots!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-taco-bowls-7aa09044.jpg
